latest_videos.video_title: Endless Spanish App Preview ~ Spanish Language
latest_videos.video_description:
Descargar aquí: https://goo.gl/aqzoPO

¡Introducir el idioma español a los niños con Endless español! Con la ayuda de los monstruos adorables de Endless, los niños se divertirán aprendiendo palabras que se utilizan con frecuencia en español, tanto su significado y ortografía como su contexto y uso. Cada palabra cuenta con un rompecabezas interactivo, con letras que cobran vida y un rompecabezas de la frase con palabras que se transforman en lo que describen. ¡Verán como la palabra "grande" se hace más grande, y como la palabra "flor" florece!

Dos modos de audio están disponibles en la aplicación: "Spanish Immersion" (inmersión en español) para hispanohablantes nativos y estudiantes avanzados, y "Spanish with English Translation” (español con traducción alinglés) para la mayoría de los anglohablantes nativos.

FREE iOS Download:  https://goo.gl/aqzoPO

Introduce the Spanish language to young children with Endless Spanish!  With the help of the adorable Endless monsters, kids will have fun learning frequently used Spanish words including context and usage!  Each word features an interactive word puzzle featuring letters that come to life, and a sentence puzzle with words that transform into what they describe.  See the word "grande" (big) grow larger, and the word "flor" (flower) open and bloom!

Two audio modes are available in the app:  "Spanish Immersion" for native Spanish speakers and advanced learners, and "Spanish with English Translation" for most native English speakers.

Download now for free: https://goo.gl/aqzoPO

From Originator, the team that brought you Endless Alphabet, Endless Spanish is an introduction to Spanish letters, phonics, and high frequency words.  Good for both native Spanish and English speakers, Endless Spanish will be available for iOS in mid May 2015.

FREE iOS Download: https://goo.gl/BTbqsB
FREE Android DOwnload: https://goo.gl/UrK33e

recommended_videos.description:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.originatorkids.EndlessAlphabet

Set the stage for reading success with this delightfully interactive educational app. Kids will have a blast learning their ABC's and building vocabulary with the adorable monsters in Endless Alphabet. Each word features an interactive puzzle with talking letters and a short animation illustrating the definition. Before you know it, your child will be using words like gargantuan and cooperate!

recommended_videos.title: MathTango: Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication & Division Fun!
recommended_videos.description:
Try it FREE on iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/mathtango-grades-k-5/id6475483877
Try it Free on Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sagosago.MathTango.googleplay

MathTango is THE definitive early math app.  Based on the Common Core standards, the comprehensive curriculum is designed to teach and reinforce early math for 5 to 10-year-olds.   MathTango reinforces addition, subtraction, multiplication and division math facts and techniques that children learn in 1st through 5th grade.   It's also the most FUN kids will have learning math!
